The paper describes the development of a bot to filter the journal impact factor rank by specific parameters, which involves automatic search and processing of results. This suggests that the paper may belong to the Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Digital Libraries (cs.DL), or Databases (cs.DB) sub-categories, which deal with search and retrieval of information. Additionally, the use of machine learning techniques to process the results may indicate a focus on Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) or Machine Learning (cs.LG).
